<item>
            <title>[LU-19453] use-after-free of lov_stripe_md</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19453</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;With the conversion to kref() a LASSERT() that prevented a UAF&lt;br/&gt;
was removed. However some callers of lsm_addref() handled this&lt;br/&gt;
case gracefully so the LASSERT() was not in the correct location.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Remove the UAF race with kref_get_unless_zero() and returning NULL.&lt;br/&gt;
Callers which cannot gracefully handle the UAF path should LASSERT()&lt;/p&gt;</description>
